## #   pv <dbl>, bounded <lgl>, OR <dbl>, ORCI <chr>, count <chr>,
## #   countCI <chr>, Thyroid_test_4 <chr>, high_low <chr>, n_cov <chr>,
## #   N_bin <fct>
overall_ci  <- 
  TSH_long %>% 
  filter(!is.na(Sig)) %>% 
  group_by(Thyroid_test) %>% 
  summarise(
    n_sig = sum(Sig == "Y"), 
    N = n(), 
    p = n_sig / N,
    lwr = p - 1.96 * sqrt(p * (1 - p) / N),
    upr = p + 1.96 * sqrt(p * (1 - p) / N)
  )
overall_ci
## # A tibble: 3 x 6
##   Thyroid_test n_sig     N     p   lwr   upr
##   <chr>        <int> <int> <dbl> <dbl> <dbl>
## 1 FT4            260   462 0.563 0.518 0.608
## 2 T3              88   174 0.506 0.431 0.580
## 3 TSH            102   462 0.221 0.183 0.259
ggplot(overall_ci, aes( Thyroid_test, p, col = Thyroid_test)) + 
  geom_point() + 
  geom_errorbar(aes(ymin = lwr, ymax = upr), width = 0.1) + 
  theme(legend.position = "none") + 
  labs(y = "Proportion")
